full_summary:
# Government Tender Announcement

## Mandatory Information
* **Reference Number**: cb-326-77784149
* **Solicitation Number**: S4725356
* **Publication Date**: 2023-11-09
* **Tender Closing Date**: 2023-11-16T15:00:
* **Contracting Entity**: Department of National Defense
* **Contracting Entity Address**: 60 Moodie Drive, Ottawa, ON K2H8G1, Canada

## Opportunity Description
The Department of National Defense (DND) is seeking temporary help services under the Supply Arrangement (SA) EN578-172870. The requirement is open only to SA holders who qualified under the following streams and categories:
 - Stream 5.1: Computer Application Support

## Notice Details
* **Type of Notice**: Request for Proposal (RFP)
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Selective Tendering
* **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price

## Security Requirements
* **Minimum Security Level Required**: Secret

## Contact Information
* **Point of Contact**: CFSG(O-G) Temp Help
* **Email**: [CFSGO-GTemporaryHelp-GSFCO-Gdaidetemporaire@forces.gc.ca](mailto:CFSGO-GTemporaryHelp-GSFCO-Gdaidetemporaire@forces.gc.ca)
* **Phone**: (613) 971-7955

## Tender Documents
The tender documents, including the request for proposal, can be accessed at:
https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/24467/s4725356-rfp-%28english_0.pdf
https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/24467/s4725356--dp-%28french_0.pdf

The contractors are required to submit a proposal in accordance with the instructions outlined in the RFP. Proposals that meet the requirements outlined in the SA EN578-172870 will be considered. The proposed contractor will be required to provide Temporary Help Services under the specified streams and categories.

The point of contact for this opportunity is CFSG(O-G) Temp Help. Please contact them to obtain further information and access the tender documents.
